Package: mlbsim
Title: A Collection of MLB Simulation Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tristan", "Hiestand", , "thiestand@elon.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: 'mlbsim' allows you to simulate MLB plate appearances, innings, 
  and games. Additionally, several data sets are included for default lineup 
  creations and the entirety of pitchers and hitters from the 2024 MLB season.
